Gold Futures Rise to Record $1,522.80 an Ounce Following Fed's Statement

-- B y   P a t r i c k   M c K i e r n a n
-- 
2011-04-27T17:43:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/gold-futures-rise-to-record-1-522-80-an-ounce-following-fed-s-statement.html
Gold futures for June delivery rose
as much as 1.3 percent to a record $1,522.80 an ounce on the
Comex in  New York .  The previous all-time high was $1,519.20 on April 25.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Patrick McKiernan at 
 pmckiernan@bloomberg.net  